data.description:
Introducing 22142 Zion Parkway, an exceptional end unit townhome nestled in the charming Oak Grove community. THREE bedrooms, TWO bathrooms, TWO car attached garage!!  This delightful residence exudes a rustic charm and offers a serene country setting. Step inside to discover vaulted ceilings on the main level, creating a spacious and airy atmosphere. The living room opens up to a delightful patio door leading to a deck that offers panoramic views of the wooded surroundings, making it the perfect spot to relax and unwind. You won't believe the size of the family room that will accommodate any size gathering! 
Notably, this townhome boasts a generous backyard area, and here's the best part – there are absolutely no restrictions on the size of your furry companions. Bring your larger dogs and cats along to enjoy this wonderful space. Nature enthusiasts will revel in the abundance of nearby trails, perfect for leisurely strolls & outdoor adventures.  **50 year shingles with warranty!!
